metadata.name: SOS WORLD
metadata.description: A group of turtles emerges from a sunken Venice. Its marvellous palaces, alleyways and bridges are only a wreckage now, a far memory like one of those little worlds usually recreated in aquariums. Although, surfacing from the water, the turtles end up in a different Venice where architectural elements - even if in their original shape - are made of iron and crystal and from here they take to new horizons.
